<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.838078>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus of Zorotypus huangi n. sp. A – B. Male, in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views. C – D. Female, in dorsal (C) and lateral (D) views. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/838078/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.838082>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological details of Zorotypus huangi n. sp. A. Head, in dorsal view, with setal pores on right half of the head capsule highlighted. B. Posterior segments of abdomen in apteron male. C. Cercus. D. Projections of abdominal tergites X – XI, in lateral view. E – G. Aedeagus, in dorsal (E), lateral (F), and ventral (G) views. Scale bars: 0.2 mm in A – B, 0.1 mm in C – G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/838082/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.838080>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Morphological details of Zorotypus huangi n. sp. A. Left mandible. B. Right mandible. C. Maxilla and maxillary palpus. D. Labial palpus. E. Antenna. F. Right hind leg. Scale bars: 0.1 mm in A – D, 0.5 mm in E – F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/838080/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

